arn how to restore your headlights to their original clarity with our step-by-step guide, covering everything from sanding to protective coating.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="mastering-headlight-restoration-from-sanding-to-coating"&gt;Mastering Headlight Restoration: From Sanding to Coating&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
